    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/7a5be90f3c8f2189c0c1f23cb1e114c3.poster.avif?t=1638219502\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/7a5be90f3c8f2189c0c1f23cb1e114c3.webm?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/7a5be90f3c8f2189c0c1f23cb1e114c3.mp4?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/250c35951f6214662c982eaf1fa087de.avif?t=1638219502\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>As humanity’s resources are running out, two astronauts set off to explore other planets to save mankind from destruction. During a routine test on their way back to Earth, spaceship Orion comes into contact with what appears to be a near miss from some debris. Or so they thought. As one of the crew begins to lose their mind, what do you do? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/65f6f2b3a647eed511838bf4112d2316.poster.avif?t=1638219502\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/65f6f2b3a647eed511838bf4112d2316.webm?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/65f6f2b3a647eed511838bf4112d2316.mp4?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prove your worth or succumb to darkness.<br><br>Enjoy a short, story-rich sci-fi horror game with psychological elements to the story in which you must come face to face with a new species and save Earth.<br><br>Enter a New Surrealistic Journey of the Unknown. A Kubrickian tale of Space &amp; Adventure into the Abyss of your mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/82f05d94bac76c726a5e4c50666218d7.avif?t=1638219502\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Dialogs, cinematics, and a deeply engaging story that plays out before you. Designed with the Boxlieter Method in mind, not only play a game that is engaging, but take part in an unknown test.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/1af890503cc358f5f2fb3e94cf243421.poster.avif?t=1638219502\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/1af890503cc358f5f2fb3e94cf243421.webm?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/1af890503cc358f5f2fb3e94cf243421.mp4?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>**Game contains hardcoded subtitles for hard of hearing**<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/3d1f0f42d7d3327bc4e8a9fdceec6137.poster.avif?t=1638219502\" width=594 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/3d1f0f42d7d3327bc4e8a9fdceec6137.webm?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803420/extras/3d1f0f42d7d3327bc4e8a9fdceec6137.mp4?t=1638219502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
